import json
with open('export_data_coursera_classcentral_Final.json') as json_file:
    data = json.load(json_file)
about=[]
id_doc=[]
for i in data['coursera']['learn']:
    if(data['coursera']['learn'][i]['language']=="English"):
        about.append(data['coursera']['learn'][i]['about'])
        id_doc.append(data['coursera']['learn'][i]['id'])
        
for i in data['coursera']['specializations']:
    if(data['coursera']['specializations'][i]['language']=="English"):
        about.append(data['coursera']['specializations'][i]['about_specialization'])
        id_doc.append(data['coursera']['specializations'][i]['id'])
        
for i in data['coursera']['professional_certificates']:
    if(data['coursera']['professional_certificates'][i]['language']=="English"):
        about.append(data['coursera']['professional_certificates'][i]['about_professional_certificate'])
        id_doc.append(data['coursera']['professional_certificates'][i]['id'])
for i in data['classcentral']:
    if(len(data['classcentral'][i]['meta_data'])>1):
        if((simple_preprocess(data['classcentral'][i]['meta_data'][1])[0])=='english'):
            about.append(data['classcentral'][i]['overview'])
            id_doc.append(data['classcentral'][i]['id'])
tokenized_list=[]
tokenized_list = [simple_preprocess(doc) for doc in about]

# Define functions for stopwords, bigrams, trigrams and lemmatization

def remove_stopwords(texts):
    return [[word for word in simple_preprocess(str(doc)) if word not in stop_words] for doc in texts]

def make_bigrams(texts):
    return [bigram_mod[doc] for doc in texts]

def make_trigrams(texts):
    return [trigram_mod[bigram_mod[doc]] for doc in texts]

def lemmatization(texts, allowed_postags=['NOUN', 'VERB']):
    """https://spacy.io/api/annotation"""
    texts_out = []
    for sent in texts:
        doc = nlp(" ".join(sent)) 
        texts_out.append([token.lemma_ for token in doc if token.pos_ in allowed_postags])
    return texts_out
